  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="/about/news/329465"> The Student Publication retrospective Who is Woo? </a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
          <label class="views-label-teaser">
        Teaser:
      </label>
                <div class="field-content"><p>The Student Publication retrospective <em>Who is Woo?</em> features a selection of publications that define the student life of Emily Carr University of Art + Design over the past 90 years. The exhibition will celebrate the artistic works and publications created by past students.</p>
<p>Come visit the library to interact and explore the rich history of Emily Carr and creativity of the students.</p>
<p>The Student Publication retrospective <em>Who is Woo?</em><br />Opening Night | Thursday, March 10, 2016 from 5 to 7pm<br />Exhibition | March 4 - 23, 2016<br />Emily Carr University Library<br />1400 Johnston Street, Granville Island</p>
</div>
