                <span class="field-content"><a href="/about/news/329222">(non)functional | Amanda Wood</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
          <label class="views-label-teaser">
        Teaser:
      </label>
                <div class="field-content"><p>Library Window Gallery<br />February 3 - 15, 2016</p>
<p>func·tion·al<br />ˈfəNG(k)SH(ə)n(ə)l/<br />adjective</p>
<p>1. of or having a special activity, purpose, or task; relating to the way in which something works or operates<br />• designed to be practical and useful, rather than attractive<br />• working or operating</p>
<a href="/about/news/329222">Read more...</a></div>
