  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="/about/news/328621">Open Access Artists&#039; Books</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
          <label class="views-label-teaser">
        Teaser:
      </label>
                <div class="field-content"><p>The Artists' Books Collection is OPEN!</p>
<p>Starting this week and every Wednesday throughout the semester our  Artists' Books co-op student, William Dereume, will host open-drawer  browsing sessions in the Artists' Books Collection.</p>
<p>Visit the Library every Wednesday between 11am - 1pm if you're curious!</p>
